text: Jakov Vranković (born 12 June 1993) is a Croatian handball player who plays for Dinamo București and the Croatian national team. He participated at the 2019 World Men's Handball Championship.2019 World Men's Handball Championship roster ==Individual awards== * Romanian Liga Națională Best Foreign Player: 2015 * Prosport All-Star Right Back of the Romanian Liga Națională: 2017 ==References== Category:Croatian male handball players Category:Sportspeople from Split, Croatia Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:Expatriate handball players Category:Croatian expatriate sportspeople in France Category:Croatian expatriate sportspeople in Hungary Category:Croatian expatriate sportspeople in Qatar Category:Croatian expatriate sportspeople in Romania Category:CS Dinamo București (men's handball) players
